Amazing Huanglong Scenic Resort 
2011-07-01 03:11:59 GMT
Located in the northwest of Sichuan Province, Huanglong Scenic Resort was famed for its colorful lakes, snow-clad mountains, valleys and virgin forests. The well-known attraction features more than 3,000 colorful ponds, sizes of which vary from a few to thousands of square meters. The water in these ponds is azure blue, pure and clear, ranging from inky to shimmering.
